#improved to cover:

#1. Terraform local directories

#2. backup files

#3. crash logs

#4. plan output

#5. variable override files

#6. lock files (optional but recommended)



# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Terraform directories
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
.terraform/
.terraform/providers/

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local Terraform state
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Sensitive variable files
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json

# Ignore override files as they are often personal/dev only
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Terraform plan & crash files
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
crash.log
crash.*.log
terraform.tfplan

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Editor & OS junk
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Terraform lock file
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Optional: ignore this if you don't want to commit the lock file
# (Most teams DO commit it, like with npm/yarn lockfiles)
#.terraform.lock.hcl